{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And- and you are-- but it came to the point that I had an injury and my-- my foot was frozen and a heavy piece of equipment fell on it in that place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my feet were swollen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I came into the-- to the-- to the camp, I still weighed 80 kilograms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here, in this-- this cold, I-- [SIGH] I-- I decided I can't carry on anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I-- I have to register-- register--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The weight, I remember when-- when I was liberated but that's-- I think I shouldn't skip this-- this one story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's important, for posterity to-- to-- to-- to-- We worked in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm coming back, because I think it's important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were suffering so badly from the cold that I thought in order to preserve some heat, body heat-- we didn't have working in that mountain.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the way, we worked for a German company called Hochtief.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That company is still in existence now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a construction company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Cement-- the cement bags was-- were closed up with-- with wires.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, like-- like you sew-- sew-- sew up at the end with tiny wires.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, some people, their-- their shoelaces were torn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they-- they used those wires that were taken off from cement bags to use it, to use it to tie their shoes because you couldn't go out and buy it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Besides, we didn't have for what to buy and what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Another thing what we did, we took out those empty cement bags.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Those were heavy bags that-- that kept 100 pounds or 120 pounds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how many pounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you cut-- we cut out holes on each side.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
